","msg":"我最多係飲到嘔，但個腦仲係好清醒，記得發生過啲乜，知自己做緊咩，係純粹個胃頂唔順<br />\n好想知斷片係咩感覺"},{"pid":"7cc6b8540b8e4d437dd59193fb31f4ec9cbd4e99","tid":316330,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最多係飲到嘔，但個腦仲係好清醒，記得發生過啲乜，知自己做緊咩，係純粹個胃頂唔順<br />\n好想知斷片係咩感覺</blockquote><br />\n啱 就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b4cbb1723d52e8137f833a15dc16ab8f8e28c7","tid":316330,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a54a90b486d4858dcfa790e29546747d8b680505","tid":316330,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我飲清15 %濃度好快就臉紅</blockquote><br />\n轉飲啤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔嘔落曬肚會有啤酒肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03854a085cc4f6dd88e8c46affb7deffd09332a2","tid":316330,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"飲到wing wing地都搭到尾班地鐵（上上落落）返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7581db7125993f8bed9175efc8b21c55b8b2a037","tid":316330,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我最多係飲到嘔，但個腦仲係好清醒，記得發生過啲乜，知自己做緊咩，係純粹個胃頂唔順<br />\n好想知斷片係咩感覺</blockquote><br />\n啱 就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲咁耐斷過一次咁大把<br />\n果陣空肚就咁隊vodka 20分鐘隊左半枝<br />\n之後嘔左兩獲就無野 果陣都知自己做緊乜 但醒左之後就無乜印象 到睇返啲相之後先記得做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5515db6f385925c1527e46d27c81fa16f009e6","tid":316330,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我最多係飲到嘔，但個腦仲係好清醒，記得發生過啲乜，知自己做緊咩，係純粹個胃頂唔順<br />\n好想知斷片係咩感覺</blockquote><br />\n啱 就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲咁耐斷過一次咁大把<br />\n果陣空肚就咁隊vodka 20分鐘隊左半枝<br />\n之後嘔左兩獲就無野 果陣都知自己做緊乜 但醒左之後就無乜印象 到睇返啲相之後先記得做過啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇發酒癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7286a2dcfcaba3a23de01b6931ed59c440e7a670","tid":316330,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我最多係飲到嘔，但個腦仲係好清醒，記得發生過啲乜，知自己做緊咩，係純粹個胃頂唔順<br />\n好想知斷片係咩感覺</blockquote><br />\n斷左片點會有感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過一次斷片 玩骰盅 猜枚 係咁輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二朝一瞓醒就係屋企地下<br />\n醒返大致都記得做過咩<br />\n但後尾個一兩粒鐘就無晒記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨記得自己個晚等的士個陣漚左次<br />\n係的士到忍住唔漚<br />\n返到屋企係𨋢口垃圾房漚左次<br />\n瞓醒睇對鞋同褲腳勁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醒返又唔見頭痛<br />\n係好口乾 同埋冇咩力 飲左兩支寶礦力 食個飯 瞓左陣就冇野"},{"pid":"7ca2a0f9abdecbb2e3062b8e4b9bda1b9a6f04b1","tid":316330,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T16:38:40.000Z","msg":"你有freestyle嗎？"},{"pid":"e87447bbafbbe91ab094e78817531ae6b53f695e","tid":316330,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:24:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2937094042f61ed65fe35e0b4c5e822897076db","tid":316330,"uid":1653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"易醉都幾好<br />\n訓到昏迷咁真係好正<br />\n好想永遠咁樣訓落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b471239aee47d939c5a5b5995ba3fa808fb37c","tid":316330,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T18:43:38.